<i>noun</i>: 허용 [허용], 양보 [양ː보] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>허용 [허용]</dt><br>
<dd>1. permission; allowing</dd><br>
<dd>문제 삼지 않고 허락하여 받아들임.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of allowing and accepting something without raising any question to it.</dd><br>
<dd>2. concession</dd><br>
<dd>주로 경기에서, 막아야 할 것을 막지 못하여 당함. 또는 그런 일.</dd><br>
<dd>Usually in a game, an act of losing by failing to defend against an attack, etc.; or such an act.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>양보 [양ː보]</dt><br>
<dd>1. concession; yielding</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람을 위해 자리나 물건 등을 내주거나 넘겨줌.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of giving up one's seat, possession, etc., for another person.</dd><br>
<dd>2. compromise; concession</dd><br>
<dd>자신의 생각이나 주장을 굽혀 남의 의견을 따름.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of changing one's thought or position, and following another person's opinion.</dd><br>
<dd>3. concession</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람을 위해 자기 자신의 이익을 포기함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of giving up one's interest for another person.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>